H0.text: In which African country is the Danikil Desert. Ethiopia

H1.text: In which African country is the Danikil Desert. Eritrea

H2.text: In which African country is the Danikil Desert. Djibouti

H3.text: In which African country is the Danikil Desert. FDRE

A4.text: The Danakil Depression is a large valley across the north of the Afar Region of Ethiopia and Eritrea.

A5.text: The Danakil Depression is located in Ethiopia and Eritrea, not in Djibouti.
